Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:22:01.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被强行拷上了手銬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:07.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看吧 愚昧的棋子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:12.18,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這定罪的把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.26,0:22:14.93,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇異的獨角戲舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:17.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你的眼睛看著 競争
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:22.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}遺落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:22.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欺騙吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.69,0:22:25.28,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多線並行的發展
