Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.07,0:22:30.78,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呼喊著 這是我正義的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:33.16,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}許下你的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:35.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}值得讚美的驚恐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:38.50,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唯獨拒絕喪失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:43.50,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}指引我吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.55,0:22:46.17,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}過於艷麗的忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:48.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}帶有偏見的分類
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.34,0:22:50.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要相信没有故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:52.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道你準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:54.47,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我們已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.47,0:22:56.47,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人人都愛著绝望
